product_desc: Quiqio, Inc (Quick I/O) is a software company that develops high performance backend technologies including Taqio. Taqio has more than twice the throughput of the leading web servers and caching proxies in the industry. Their technology uses less data center power as it keeps CPU utilization at a minimum. It is highly scalable and available, thereby maximizing uptime. Taqio automatically detects and uses optimal settings for the host. It is easy and fast to deploy. Using Taqio can help companies reduce data-center operational costs and serve content faster than anyone. It runs on all major operating systems and can help CDNs run more efficiently and serve content faster.
name: QuiqIO
